{"tid":1124752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先後虛報葵涌有人自殺及打架　警追緝報假案無聊人","createTime":"2019-04-25T08:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T01:35:07.000Z","uid":19552,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d92d716f6fac64631d96304e829ea2e7eaf95f1","tid":1124752,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"昨日傍晚約6時，警方先接獲有人報案，指葵涌葵聯路一間學校，有人企圖自殺；隨後又指該學校有人打架。警方到場搜索並無發現；未幾，警方又接獲報案指，葵涌葵富路一間食店有人打架，警方隨即派員趕到現場，惟亦是撲空。經初步調查，相信以上案件均為惡意虛報電話，案件列作「浪費警力」，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕，正追查報假案人士身份及下落。"},{"pid":"42e10d1d48f6b3ead6bfffdf03024367a2798f50","tid":1124752,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>實捉到你</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3d5772f1c401867a4332f8456254518beefe390e","tid":1124752,"uid":223256,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"你點知人地無打?<br />\n打完一早走左啦<br />\n等比人拉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6da95744abaa55231f522859dbb6a5859fe02d","tid":1124752,"uid":221136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"蓋係咪喺葵廣鞋店做sales"},{"pid":"5c5949f8875500a3627822dcba05928de58472d9","tid":1124752,"uid":160662,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3d5772f1c401867a4332f8456254518beefe390e","tid":1124752,"uid":223256,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"你點知人地無打?<br />\n打完一早走左啦<br />\n等比人拉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"係你咁白痴先唔識分辨既啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校得呢幾條友? 食店老闆伙記去左邊???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec36649a46f153ee15def772829b8ad041c50b7","tid":1124752,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit